Package: open-omniscience
Version: 0.02-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Open-Omniscience Team <team@ideotion.com>
Description: Open-Omniscience - Ethical Global Intelligence Platform
 Open-Omniscience is an open-source, ethical, global intelligence platform
 for investigative journalism. It aggregates raw news information from
 diverse worldwide sources into a unified, highly searchable, and
 auditable database.
 .
 Features:
  - Cross-reference disparate pieces of information
  - Identify complex patterns and disinformation schemes
  - Preserve data integrity and provenance
  - Local LLM support for analysis and synthesis
  - Built on Python with Docker support

Depends: docker.io, docker-compose, git, curl, python3, python3-venv, python3-pip
Homepage: https://github.com/ideotion/Open-Omniscience
